                "url": "https://defector.com/incoming-tnr-editor-lays-out-boring-vision-for-magazine-in-depressing-meeting-with-staff/",
                "version": 1
              },
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": ". There's a clear trend developing of staff who are not happy about an incoming editor making it know through both social media and other publications. I'm not sure this will have the same impact as the ",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              },
              {
