          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", would like to remind her fellow journalists that the restrictions on overseas travel aren't just about holidays: they're keeping families apart. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "bookmark",
        "url": "https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/international-travel-restrictions-families-lockdown-b1823082.html#comments-area",
        "metadata": {
          "url": "https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/international-travel-restrictions-families-lockdown-b1823082.html",
          "title": "Opinion: International travel restrictions stop more than just holidays",
          "description": "Millions of people are missing a lot more than a tan and a poolside cocktail, for transnational families there‚Äôs no end to lockdown",
